# HPN Tunnel Public Repository - Strict Protection
# This repo is a PUBLIC SHOWROOM ONLY - NO source code should ever be committed

# Block ALL files by default
*
!*/

# ONLY allow these specific files and directories
!README.md
!LICENSE
!INSTALL.md
!BUILD.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!.gitignore

# Allow assets directory and common image formats
!assets/
!assets/**/*.png
!assets/**/*.jpg
!assets/**/*.jpeg
!assets/**/*.svg
!assets/**/*.ico
!assets/**/*.gif

# Allow install scripts (if added later)
!install.sh
!install.ps1

# Block ALL source code and build artifacts
*.go
go.mod
go.sum
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.a
*.o
*.obj
*.lib

# Block all build and development directories
dist/
build/
bin/
obj/
vendor/
node_modules/
.git/
.github/
.vscode/
.idea/

# Block all common source code patterns
*.c
*.cpp
*.h
*.hpp
*.java
*.py
*.js
*.ts
*.tsx
*.jsx
*.rb
*.php
*.rs
*.swift
*.kt

# Block configuration that might leak info
*.env
*.env.*
.env.local
.env.production
config.yaml
config.json
secrets.*

# Block any archives (to prevent accidental source dumps)
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.rar
*.7z
